{"tid":1893983,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[舔共］張學友新歌為醫護打氣, 承諾以「不添亂」態度防疫 環球點名感謝曾志偉","createTime":"2020-02-23T15:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T16:13:46.000Z","uid":8410,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"972da8d84e69e9802a582280cf75db2897c0177e","tid":1893983,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cheung-16_m2r7i_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcheung-16_m2r7i_1200x0.png&h=71a06f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐，接連有歌手用音樂為大家打氣。舔共偽人張學友今早推出國語歌曲《等風雨經過》，並由台灣共諜周杰倫作曲、方文山填詞，為前缐醫護打氣。張學友在MV中承諾以<span style=\"color: red;\">「不自私、不添亂」態度防疫，而唱片公司環球則特別點名多謝曾志偉協助</span>。<br />\n今日環球音樂在FB發表了《等風雨經過》的MV，影片主要<span style=\"color: red;\">由內地醫護人員的畫面剪輯而成</span>。<br />\n張學友在片尾中表示，人的善與美，在面對困境與艱難時刻最能體現，謹此向所有勇敢在前線抗疫救人的醫護人員致以最崇高的敬意，「我張學友承諾做好個人衞生，<span style=\"color: red;\">懷着不自私、不添亂的態度</span>，防止疫情擴散，保障好每個社區、每個家園，大家一定要平安健康回家」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%BC%B5%E5%AD%B8%E5%8F%8B%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%8C%E7%82%BA%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3-%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E4%BB%A5-%E4%B8%8D%E6%B7%BB%E4%BA%82-%E6%85%8B%E5%BA%A6%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB-%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E9%BB%9E%E5%90%8D%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25AD%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E6%2585%258B%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAymzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=f73d563b\" data-ef-url=\"htt